polls in the state. [NAN] Vanguard News Nigeria. ASABA—AHEAD of the Delta State Local Government elections slated for January 6, 2018, the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, has pegged chairmanship and councillorship nomination forms at N1 million and N200,000 respectively. October 9, 2017 In "News" FOLLOWING, the issuance of guidelines for the July 22 local council poll by the Lagos State Independent Electoral Commission, LASIEC, there is a rat race in the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC, for the chairmanship and councilorship slots. So far, the party has screened 450 chairmanship and 1,300 councilorship aspirants. May 13, 2017 In "News" The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP has won 23 local government council chairmanship and 239 of the 244 councillorship positions in an election in which 33 political parties participated. July 25, 2011 In "News"